{"title":"颂歌","authors":["赛福鼎·艾则孜"],"dates":[{"year":1991,"month":9,"day":30}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"颂歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赛福鼎·艾则孜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“东方红”，“太阳升”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国晴空红旗飘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗光辉照大地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“百万工农齐踊跃”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中华苦难的大地上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"星星之火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燃起熊熊燎原大火。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“中国出了个毛泽东”！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他是人民忠诚的儿子。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他高举红缨发号召："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"起来！是时候了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这号召，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宣判了凶神恶煞的死刑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宣告了无产者的新生。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战斗——前进！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前进——战斗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苦难人民渴望的日子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终于来临。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“四海翻腾云水怒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五洲震荡风雷激”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大地在震颤，山岳在摇撼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄健儿齐上阵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前仆后继，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"接过红旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终于摧毁了敌人的宝座。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"领袖宣告："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“中国人民站起来了！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天安门广场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五星红旗高高飘扬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一宣告声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"响彻九霄云天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回荡在古老东方的土地上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这声音——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是争得解放"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掌握自己命运的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大民族的胜利凯歌！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这声音，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越过高山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跨过海洋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在世界各地回荡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们知道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树欲静而风不止，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那贪婪的目光在窥视我们；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狡猾的狐狸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"急不可耐地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不停地走动。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正告这些先生们："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们将永远前进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绝不后退，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"接过前辈未尽的事业，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无数后辈定将继续奋进。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"道路是伟大的。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们有的是——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"颗颗红心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚定的意志。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们决心："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将血染的红旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"插在高山的顶峰！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}